================================================================================
Context: The breadcrumb bar added between the navbar and the content wrapper
introduced ~35px of extra height that was not accounted for in the sidebar
layout sizing (hardcoded calc(100vh - 60px)). This caused a small vertical
scroll on every page where the breadcrumb is visible.

